h           (N): Move left
j           (N): Move down
k           (N): Move up
l           (N): Move right
i           (N): Insert text
a           (N): Append text
x           (N): Delete character
dd          (N): Delete a line
J           (N): Join lines
u           (N): Undo a change
CTRL-R      (N): Redo a change
ZZ          (N): Writes the file and exits

            Moving Around
$           (N): Moves to the cursor to the end of a line
^           (N): Moves to the first non-blank character of the line
0           (N): Mobes to the very first character of the line

